    <h2 id="mileStones">Part 2: Transcription Milestones</h2>
    <p>You think it’s a long way to the chip shop... FreeBMD is big. Really big! It was anticipated that it would take a decade to complete a ‘first keying’- <mark> I will, sometime, say what this means, or add hyperlink. It was in the draft FAQ page I produced but it has edited out, by re-wording - PC </mark> -  from the start of the index in 1837 to the end of 1901.</p>                     

    <p class="push-half--bottom">This target was substantially achieved in July 2005. But even in the first few years, the website was already being useful to researchers. Of course, the more people help, the sooner it will be completed.</p> 
