   <h3 id="AncestryBuyMicrofilms">Ancestry purchase for our use a complete set of G.R.O. Index microfilms for 1837 to 1900 </h3>
    <p> On <strong>9 January 2001</strong>, FreeBMD were very pleased to record that Ancestry has very kindly purchased a complete set of Birth, Marriage and Death G.R.O. Index microfilms, for years 1837 to 1900, for our use.  We are now working to ensure that data of higher quality will be available for transcribers.</p> 
  
